Description: This package aims at regroupping essential tools for credit scoring. These statistical tools may be useful for other use-cases as well but were primarly designed for it. First, there are Reject Inference methods' functions <>. Second, we build upon the already CRAN-available package "discretization" and "glmdisc" to . Third, we provide a way.
